<li id="cite_note-Alexander-12"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Alexander_12-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREFPritchard2005">Pritchard, Claudia (2005-03-27). <a href="http://enjoyment.independent.co.uk/books/features/article8437.ece" class="external text" title="http://enjoyment.independent.co.uk/books/features/article8437.ece" rel="nofollow">"His dark materials"</a>. The Independent<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://enjoyment.independent.co.uk/books/features/article8437.ece" class="external free" title="http://enjoyment.independent.co.uk/books/features/article8437.ece" rel="nofollow">http://enjoyment.independent.co.uk/books/features/article8437.ece</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2006-07-23</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=His+dark+materials&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Pritchard&amp;rft.aufirst=Claudia&amp;rft.au=Pritchard%2C+Claudia&amp;rft.date=2005-03-27&amp;rft.pub=The+Independent&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fenjoyment.independent.co.uk%2Fbooks%2Ffeatures%2Farticle8437.ece&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Hans_Christian_Andersen"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Guardian-13"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Guardian_13-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREFLepage2006">Lepage, Robert (2006-01-18). <a href="http://books.guardian.co.uk/departments/classics/story/0,6000,1689053,00.html" class="external text" title="http://books.guardian.co.uk/departments/classics/story/0,6000,1689053,00.html" rel="nofollow">"Bedtime stories"</a>. The Guardian<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://books.guardian.co.uk/departments/classics/story/0,6000,1689053,00.html" class="external free" title="http://books.guardian.co.uk/departments/classics/story/0,6000,1689053,00.html" rel="nofollow">http://books.guardian.co.uk/departments/classics/story/0,6000,1689053,00.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2006-07-19</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Bedtime+stories&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Lepage&amp;rft.aufirst=Robert&amp;rft.au=Lepage%2C+Robert&amp;rft.date=2006-01-18&amp;rft.pub=The+Guardian&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbooks.guardian.co.uk%2Fdepartments%2Fclassics%2Fstory%2F0%2C6000%2C1689053%2C00.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Hans_Christian_Andersen"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Garfield-14"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Garfield_14-0" title="">^</a></b> Recorded using "special Greek symbols".<cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFGarfield2004">Garfield, Patricia (2004-06-21). <a href="http://www.patriciagarfield.com/publications/anderson_2004IASD.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.patriciagarfield.com/publications/anderson_2004IASD.pdf" rel="nofollow">"The Dreams of Hans Christian Andersen"</a> (PDF). 29<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.patriciagarfield.com/publications/anderson_2004IASD.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.patriciagarfield.com/publications/anderson_2004IASD.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.patriciagarfield.com/publications/anderson_2004IASD.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2006-07-20</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+Dreams+of+Hans+Christian+Andersen&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Garfield&amp;rft.aufirst=Patricia&amp;rft.au=Garfield%2C+Patricia&amp;rft.date=2004-06-21&amp;rft.pages=29&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.patriciagarfield.com%2Fpublications%2Fanderson_2004IASD.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Hans_Christian_Andersen"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Bryant-15">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Bryant_15-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Bryant_15-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> Bryant, Mark: <i>Private Lives</i>, 2001, p.12</li>
<li id="cite_note-16"><b><a href="#cite_ref-16" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/4782955.stm" class="external text" title="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/4782955.stm" rel="nofollow">China to open Andersen theme park</a>, <i>BBC News</i>, <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2006-08-11"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="08-11"><a href="/wiki/August_11" title="August 11">August 11</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2006" title="2006">2006</a></span>. Accessed <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2008-07-02"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="07-02"><a href="/wiki/July_2" title="July 2">July 2</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2008" title="2008">2008</a></span>.</li>
<li id="cite_note-17"><b><a href="#cite_ref-17" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://puppet.org/perform/snowman.shtml" class="external text" title="http://puppet.org/perform/snowman.shtml" rel="nofollow">", "Jon Ludwig's 'Sam the Lovesick Snowman'"</a></li>
