<li id="cite_note-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.liornavok.com/music.asp?name=The+Little+Mermaid+%2D+for+chamber+ensemble+%2F+orchestra&amp;id=75" class="external text" title="http://www.liornavok.com/music.asp?name=The+Little+Mermaid+%2D+for+chamber+ensemble+%2F+orchestra&amp;id=75" rel="nofollow">", "Lior Navok's 'The Little Mermaid'"</a></li>
